# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Secrets & environment  ── NEVER commit these. (Spec §3.3)
# API keys, the Autotask secret/integration code, GHL OAuth client secret and
# tokens, and DB connection strings must never enter Git history. They live in a
# git-ignored .env locally, and in Azure Key Vault in production.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.key
*.pem

# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.venv/
venv/
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/

# IDE / OS
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Local DB / logs
*.sqlite3
*.log
pgdata/

# Build / dist
dist/
build/
